{"tid":2237771,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"其實識玩應該鬥紅，然後互相舉報唔夠紅既藍官同藍教師","createTime":"2020-10-10T14:10:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T12:20:25.000Z","uid":273218,"like":31,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"f1300db6286f3106358425f83173b243ad3bdb93","tid":2237771,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T14:10:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=408515\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D408515&d=qh2qPVBUtyR5HqmPKg%2BIDFSbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=01536e8b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D408515&h=74dd8387\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=408515</a><br />\n楊潤雄：教育局正跟進一至兩宗投訴老師的相對嚴重個案<br />\n10小時前 Share to Facebook<br />\n【Now新聞台】教育局取消九龍塘宣道小學一名教師的註冊，指其在教材散播港獨信息。教育局局長楊潤雄強調事件不涉及政治考慮，他又透露局方正跟進一至兩宗相對嚴重的個案，但仍需時間考慮是否取消相關教<br />\n<br />\n如果鬥紅，香港會進入真正文革時期<br />\n經濟會大幅下滑<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n師的註冊。"},{"pid":"4df8039d0458acdac809de59a28f0834eb750bb9","tid":2237771,"uid":273218,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T14:11:00.000Z","msg":"如果鬥紅，香港會進入真正文革時期"},{"pid":"3d30941dcdeeb3a637b76512703a349cba26800e","tid":2237771,"uid":30910,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T14:12:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"164c9f1b1b90511ce8dc43984755bfb3677a07a7","tid":2237771,"uid":59976,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T14:14:49.000Z","msg":"支持加速攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2ik2dAo.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2ik2dAo.gif&h=ce5a5ebd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7kPa6Vo.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7kPa6Vo.gif&h=db02d579&s={SIZ